  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ ひらぬま・きいちろう ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n<a href=\"../1939/hira_1.html\">首相</a>、法相、枢密院議長、司法次官、検事総長、国本社社主、Ａ級戦犯"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"06h.html\">一覧　（ハ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B2%25BC%2520%25E9%25A8%258F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2583%258E\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　岡山県出身。津山藩士の家に生まれる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　帝大卒業後、判事、東京控訴院部長を経て検事に転じる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　司法次官、検事総長、大審院長を歴任後、<a href=\"../1923/yamm2_1.html\">山本内閣②</a>の法相に就任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　虎の門事件に衝撃を受け国本社を結成、皇室中心主義を主張。隠然たる勢力を築く。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　国本社を解散し、枢密院議長に就任。<a href=\"../1937/kono1_1.html\">近衛内閣①</a>のあと、首相就任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1940/09jdi_d.html\">日独伊三国軍事同盟締結</a>に腐心するうち、<a href=\"../1939/05nomon.html\">ノモンハン事件</a>が発生。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　続いて<a href=\"../1939/08ds_jy.html\">独ソ不可侵条約</a>が結ばれるや、「複雑怪奇」の流行語を残して<a href=\"../1939/hira_9.html\">総辞職</a>。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　他の重臣とともに、東條内閣倒閣、終戦工作を推進。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、Ａ級戦犯として東京裁判で「終身禁固」の判決。服役中に病死。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
